section.para:
Here's an example that creates a compound index of
      lastName in ascending order and age in
      descending order: 
          Example Compound Index Usage

          package com.mycompany.domain;

@Document
@CompoundIndexes({
    @CompoundIndex(name = "age_idx", def = "{'lastName': 1, 'age': -1}")
})
public class Person {

  @Id
  private ObjectId id;
  private Integer age;
  private String firstName;
  private String lastName;

}

